  autocmd!
  autocmd FileType markdown,mkd  call pencil#init()
  autocmd FileType text          call pencil#init()
augroup END
" Pencil - initialise pencil
" NoPencil - restore to global settings
" TogglePencil or PencilToggle
" PencilSoft / PencilHard

